ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
SubjectIssuance of two $1 circulation coins with a design commemorating the 75th anniversary of the United Nations Charter
PrecisOrder Authorizing the ISSUANCE of two $1 circulation coins with a design commemorating the 75th anniversary of the of the United Nations Charter in order to raise awareness and serve as tangible keepsakes of Canada's contributions to the United Nations and to the country's ongoing commitment to the organization's principles.
